  PIXEL QUOTE MAX — Product & Pricing Database
  ============================================
  This file is the SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for all prices and product specs.
  Edit values here and refresh the app — no code changes needed.

  • rate   = INR per square foot of LED
  • gst    = GST % for that pitch
  • controllers / installTiers = priced in INR
